==Daily==
===(Trailblazer), I finished reading...===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Jing Yuan:''' (Trailblazer), I finished reading the files that you shared with me from the data bank.
:'''Jing Yuan:''' After sitting in this Seat of Divine Foresight for so long, I can't help but overlook the world outside of Luofu's delves.<br />That, combined with the long lifespan of the Xianzhou humans, made me feel that the entire world is as boring and changeless as myself.<br />However, now I've read the wondrous encounters of the Express Crew, I realized that using my endless lifespan to travel various worlds would be a fun venture indeed.
:'''Jing Yuan:''' Unfortunately... I still shoulder Luofu's countless duties and cannot accompany your group. But if I were to retire one day, what should I do?
:{Choice} Become a Nameless
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Our Express is pretty big. You can come visit, general
::'''Jing Yuan:''' Hahahaha, if that's a personal invitation, (Trailblazer), then I might consider it.
:{Choice} Take Fu Xuan's job
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Perhaps you can swap places with Fu Xuan and be the master diviner
::'''Jing Yuan:''' Hahaha, don't ever mention that to me again. The master diviner is an exceedingly busy job. No ordinary person can face its arduous work.
:{Choice} Work for the Realm-Keeping Commission
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I feel the Realm-Keeping Commission's work is quite relaxed...
::'''Jing Yuan:''' Hahaha, that would truly take me back to my origins.
::'''Jing Yuan:''' My parents were scholars of the Realm-Keeping Commission and were responsible for researching and recording the histories of long-life species. The paperwork involved was literal torment.
:'''Jing Yuan:''' That reminds me... My dream as a young boy was to become a Galaxy Ranger.
:'''Jing Yuan:''' Pity that life never goes the way you want it to go.
:{Choice} If given the chance...
:'''(Trailblazer):''' If given the chance, where would you want to go?
:'''Jing Yuan:''' Perhaps I'll go seek out animals that have already gone extinct in Xianzhou.
:'''Jing Yuan:''' Let us stop for today. Qingzu just carried in another pile of documents for me. Just looking at them gives me a headache.
:{Choice} You're working hard, general!
:'''(Trailblazer):''' You're working hard, general!
:'''(Trailblazer):''' I'm sorry I can't be of help...
:'''Jing Yuan:''' It's enough for me to squeeze out some time to chat with you, (Trailblazer).
:'''Jing Yuan:''' All in all, I shall return to work. Farewell!
}}
