===(Trailblazer), I have a...===
{{Messages|text=
:'''Jing Yuan:''' (Trailblazer), I have a rather abrupt request.
:{Choice} Please let me hear it, general!
:'''(Trailblazer):''' Please let me hear it, general!
:'''Jing Yuan:''' When you are free, could you please spend some time sparring with Yanqing?
:{Choice} I wouldn't dare!
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I've heard about Yanqing's sword skills and how he learned those from you, general
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I wouldn't dare to spar with him
::'''Jing Yuan:''' Haha, is that so? You are exceedingly humble.
:{Choice} I can, but...
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I can, but...
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I heard that you are his teacher, general...
::'''Jing Yuan:''' That is true. What of it?
:{Choice} Who's Yanqing?
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Who's Yanqing?
::'''Jing Yuan:''' My disciple and also a lieutenant of the Cloud Knights.
:{Choice} Then, can I spar with...
:'''(Trailblazer):''' Then, can I spar with you first?
:'''(Trailblazer):''' That way, you also get to test my capabilities
:'''Jing Yuan:''' Haha, I am already well aware of your capabilities, (Trailblazer).
:{Choice} Oh my. You saw through me
::'''(Trailblazer):''' Oh my. You saw through me
::'''(Trailblazer):''' You've exposed the fact that I don't know how to use a sword at all
::'''(Trailblazer):''' [[File:Sticker PPG 07 Pom-Pom 02.png|80px|&lbrack;cry&rbrack;]]
::'''Jing Yuan:''' You don't use a sword, and therefore don't abide by the rules and conventions of a sword fight. For Yanqing to try his skills against such an opponent would be a supreme opportunity.
:{Choice} I am indeed very strong
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I am indeed very strong
::'''(Trailblazer):''' I didn't think you'd see through me this quickly, general
::'''(Trailblazer):''' [[File:Sticker PPG 07 Pom-Pom 08.png|80px|&lbrack;Shocked&rbrack;]]
::'''Jing Yuan:''' That's to be expected. Strength does not only constitute just your physical power, skill, or weapon. It's also a matter of wisdom and tenacity. My instincts as a war veteran are to be trusted.
:'''Jing Yuan:''' As for a spar between you and me... perhaps it's better to plan for that after you've sparred with Yanqing.
:'''Jing Yuan:''' However, I have one request. If you cannot agree to it, (Trailblazer), then we cannot fight.
:{Choice} Please let me hear it, general!
:'''(Trailblazer):''' Please let me hear it, general!
:'''Jing Yuan:''' Do not book our spar for the afternoon. That time is far too tiring and sleepy.
}}
